      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUNSET AGRIPPINA (4) jumped from a squeeze box last start but was quickly into stride and led throughout to score (22.57) at this track in a Grade 5/6 over 400m. Won at her only start from this draw. Great chance to get the job done again. GEORDIE LAD (8) was in the minors when resuming at this track where he finished third (22.80) in a Grade 5. Sure to be fitter. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Must be included in calculations. KAADADJAN (1) collided in the run and missed the frame when fifth (23.08) at this track over 400m in a Grade 5. Bold showing expected on best. FERNANDO FUN (2) gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.",
